metadata.name: SLUM CITY
metadata.description:
SLUM CITY - direct inspiration from mercenaries in old retro movies to the subtle pose reference from the iconic "kill bill", this is the second character design in the series where i try to push off conventional character design on itself.
the make-believe devil in the series spotting signs of a detachable horn as an accessory with the funky hairstyle that adds as complete contrast to what the character stands for.
